      <node TEXT="Also  these algorithms have been applied for many prediction pur  poses in the medical field such as breast cancer  diabetes  and other  diseases. The propsed models in this work were implemented using Python  programming language which provides several tools for machine  learning tasks. The trees protect each  other from their flaws  which explains why they have such a strong ef  fect." />
